file.name: string-test.yml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    # String
    ko_string_wild:
      description: lacks everything
      type: string
    ko_string_no_pattern: &basestring
      type: string
      maxLength: 1
    ok_empty_string:
      type: string
      maxLength: 0
      pattern: ''
    ok_string_pattern_format:
      <<: *basestring
      pattern: '[a-z]+'
      format: email
    ok_string_datetime:
      type: string
      format: 'date-time'
    ok_string_date:
      type: string
      format: 'date'
    ok_pattern:
      <<: *basestring
      pattern: '[a-z]+'
    ok_format:
      <<: *basestring
      format: date-time
    ok_enum:
      description: |-
        Enum don't need maxLength/pattern/format
      type: string
      enum:
        - "one"
        - "two"
        - "three"
openapi: 3.0.1
paths:
  /string-ko-params:
    parameters:
      - name: ko_1
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: ciao
